			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td><a href="http://hackage.haskell.org/platform/new/contents.html">Haskell: Batteries Included</a></td>
				<td>Set of resources for learning and teaching Haskell.</td>
			</tr>
			
			<tr><th>Java</th></tr>
